 《起跑线》对泰勒·斯威夫特的《黑狗》歌词做出了回应，歌词中关于她的关系“交织在一起” https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-starting-line-react-to-taylor-swifts-the-black-dog-lyric-about-being-intertwined-in-her-relationship-3749308？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=与泰勒·斯威夫特的黑狗歌词有关在她的关系中交织在一起的起始线反应Liberty DunworthMon, 22 Apr 2024 10:18:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3749308 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《起跑线》的肯尼·瓦索里和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她在“The Tortured Poets Department”的一首曲目中提到了该乐队</p><p>这篇文章<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-starting-line-react-to-taylor-swifts-the-black-dog-lyric-about-being-intertwined-in-her-relationship-3749308">《起跑线》对泰勒·斯威夫特在《黑狗》中关于她的关系“交织在一起”的歌词做出了回应，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="《起跑线》的肯尼·瓦索里和泰勒·斯威夫特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Starting-Line-Swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454">《折磨诗人部》</a>中提到起跑线后，起跑线做出了回应。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/taylor-swift-the-tortured-poets-department-lyrics-tracklist-3619454"><b>《受折磨的诗人部》评论：罕见的失误</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该乐队在情感民谣《The Black Dog》中得到了这位流行偶像的点名——这首歌出现在她专辑的四个豪华版之一中，并且是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-tortured-poets-department-album-the-anthology-3619877">《The Tortured Poets Department: The Anthology》</a>中的第 17 首歌。 。</p><p>这首歌于上周（4 月 19 日）发布，斯威夫特回忆起她的一位前情人如何忘记禁用手机上的位置跟踪功能，并描绘了她认为他在他们的关系破裂后正在做的事情的画面。</p><p> “<em>我只是不明白/你怎么在《黑狗》中不想念我/当有人演奏《起跑线》时/你跳了起来，但她太年轻/不知道这首交织在一起的歌曲/在神奇的结构中我们的梦想</em>，”她在副歌中唱道，指的是伦敦一家酒吧里的前情人。</p><p> “<em>我希望《黑狗》里的内容很糟糕/当有人演奏《起跑线》时/你跳了起来，但她太年轻/不知道这首歌交织在一起/在我们梦想的悲剧结构中/因为尾巴夹在你的两腿之间，你要走了，</em> ”她后来继续唱道，把她的沮丧情绪变成了愤怒。 </p><p><iframe title="泰勒·斯威夫特 - The Black Dog（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/56TZ3B8Qxsk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，随着这首歌于周五发行，这支 00 年代的美国流行朋克乐队在社交媒体上分享了最新消息，感谢斯威夫特对他们的赞扬并向她的歌迷介绍了他们的唱片。</p><p> “亲爱的泰勒，我们听到了这首歌，感谢您检查我们乐队的名字。我们对由此带来的爱的回响感到受宠若惊和谦卑，”他们写道。 “很荣幸能用如此可爱的歌曲来纪念谢瑞麟。您不必这样做，但您确实这样做了，我们衷心感谢您。尊重！”</p><p>正如<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/taylor-swift-the-black-dog-the-starting-line-song-1235662129/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>所强调的，虽然斯威夫特没有提及她在歌词中指的是《起跑线》中的哪首歌，但这句台词很可能暗指乐队首张专辑《Say It Like You》中的主打单曲《The Best Of Me》意思是&#39;。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-taylor-swift-wrote-the-tortured-poets-department-about-matty-healy-3619865">据推测，这张专辑的大部分内容都是关于 1975 年的主唱马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy)</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-music-undergoes-streaming-rise-amid-reports-of-taylor-swift-romance-3443019">去年他和斯威夫特有过一段短暂的关系</a>。更重要的是，在去年的巡演中，希利两次现场演奏了《The Best Of Me》的片段——一次在新西兰，另一次在菲律宾。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C59Od2bSn1o/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.