ps://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/cities-skylines-2-refunds-rushed-dlc-and-delays-console-release-3619933">该团队为“仓促”的资料片道歉，并向玩家退款</a>，然后推迟了<em>《城市：天际线 2》</em>的主机发布，并承诺在玩家基础上做得更好。</p><p>在其他新闻中，许多在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Amazon Prime Video</a>的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/fallout">《辐射》</a></em>原声带中亮相的艺术家的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fallout-tv-series-causes-music-streams-to-double-3749274">流媒体数量急剧增加。</a></p><p>继《城市：天际线 2》问题首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/gaming-news/prison-architect-2-delayed-by-3-months-following-cities-skylines-2-issues-3749309">后，《监狱建筑师 2》的帖子延迟了三个月</a>。</p> ;
