 月发行第二张录音室专辑《The World EP.Fin: Will》之后，该专辑以主打歌《Crazy Form》为主打。</p><p> ATEEZ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coachella-2024-lineup-kpop-le-sserafim-ateez-yoasobi-88rising-3571874">在 4 月 19 日第二个周末在 Coachella 音乐节上表演</a>后，宣布推出新音乐也引起了热议。他们在这一标志性音乐节上的亮相使他们成为第一个登上科切拉舞台的韩国流行男孩乐队。</p><p>在其他韩国流行音乐新闻中，aespa 今天还宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aespa-first-studio-album-armageddon-3749198">即将发行《Armageddon》，这是他们自 2020 年出道以来的首张完整专辑</a>。与此同时，女团<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cherry-bullet">Cherry Bullet</a>的经纪公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fnc-entertainment">FNC Entertainment</a>证实已正式解散。</p><p>在其他地方，据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hybe">HYBE</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ador">ADOR</a>首席执行官 Min Hee-jin（流行女子组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans 的</a>幕后主使）正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hybe-min-hee-jin-power-struggle-over-newjeans-agency-ador-3749193">围绕这家韩国流行音乐经纪公司展开权力斗争</a>。消息传出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hybe-stock-price-dips-after-audit-of-newjeans-agency-ador-3749251">HYBE 股价下跌逾 7%</a> 。</p><p>邮报<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ateez-mini-album-golden-hour-part-1-3749237">ATEEZ 宣布新迷你专辑《Golden Hour: Part》。 1’，下个月发布，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 为奥斯卡颁奖典礼增添了爱尔兰最高表演奖https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-irish-acting-prize-oppenheimer-oscars-3749256?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cillian-murphy-irish-acting-prize-oppenheimer-oscarsAlex Berry Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:06:59 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3749256 <p><img width="1984" height="1260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards.jpg 1984w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1984px) 100vw, 1984px" /></p><p>这位演员凭借在《奥本海默》中的表演再次获得奖项</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-irish-acting-prize-oppenheimer-oscars-3749256">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 为奥斯卡颁奖典礼增添爱尔兰最高表演奖的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1984" height="1260" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="希里安·墨菲" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards.jpg 1984w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Cillian-Murphy-awards-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1984px) 100vw, 1984px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲</a>凭借在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>中的表演再次获得奖项。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片就像一颗炸弹击中大脑</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位演员最近因在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>广受好评的传记片中饰演理论物理学家 J·罗伯特·奥本海默而于周六（4 月 20 日）爱尔兰电影电视学院奖上被评为最佳男主角。</p><p>在此之前，这位演员在本颁奖季获得了一系列令人印象深刻的奖项，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-dedicates-oscars-win-peacemakers-everywhere-3599363">奥斯卡奖</a>、英国电影和电视艺术学院奖、金球奖和美国演员工会奖。</p><p>这位爱尔兰演员曾与诺兰合作过六部电影，其中包括《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-dark-knight"><em>黑暗骑士》</em></a>三部曲，他承认在祖国获得该奖项的重要性。</p><p>在被<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/killers-of-the-flower-moon"><em>《花月杀手》主演</em></a>、最佳国际女演员提名者莉莉·格莱斯顿颁奖后，墨菲在接受这一荣誉时说道：“天哪，我在这方面还是太残忍了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3749268" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3749268" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3749268" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy.jpg" alt="莉莉·格莱斯顿" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Lily-Gladstone-Cillian-Murphy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3749268" class="wp-caption-text">莉莉·格莱斯顿 (Lily Gladstone) 于 2024 年 3 月 10 日在加利福尼亚州好莱坞。图片来源：盖蒂 / 摄影：Frederic J. Brown / 法新社</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道：“但来到这个房间真是太特别了——就像在家里一样，和我所爱和钦佩的人在一起，还有我的提名者同伴和一些我最喜欢的人。”</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/awards/global/cillian-murphy-ifta-awards-2024-winners-1235977473/"><em>《综艺》</em></a>报道，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/peaky-blinders"><em>《浴血黑帮》的</em></a>明星在都柏林皇家会议中心举行的颁奖典礼结束后在后台发表讲话，分享道：“和这么多朋友和同事一起回家的感觉真好。”</p><p>与墨菲一起获得该类别提名的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/all-of-us-strangers-review-paul-mescal-andrew-scott-claire-foy-3576917"><em>《我们都是陌生人</em></a>》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andrew-scott">安德鲁·斯科特</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/saltburn"><em>索尔特伯恩</em></a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/barry-keoghan">巴里·基奥根</a>。前<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/james-bond"><em>詹姆斯·邦德</em></a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pierce-brosnan">皮尔斯·布鲁斯南</a>也因<em>《最后的步枪手》</em>获得提名。</p><p><em>奥本海默</em>还获得了最佳男配角奖，肯尼思·布拉纳因饰演物理学家尼尔斯·玻尔而获得提名。布拉纳最终输给了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mescal">保罗·梅斯卡尔</a>，后者凭借<em>《我们都是陌生人》</em>获得了该奖项。 </p><figure id="attachment_3749270" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3749270" style="width: 1435px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3749270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy.jpg" alt="安德鲁·斯科特·保罗·梅斯卡尔" width="1435" height="911" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy.jpg 1435w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Andrew-Scott-Cillian-Murphy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1435px) 100vw, 1435px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3749270" class="wp-caption-text">安德鲁·斯科特 (Andrew Scott) 和保罗·麦斯卡 (Paul Mescal) 于 2024 年 1 月 23 日在英国伦敦。图片来源：盖蒂/约翰·菲利普斯/盖蒂图片社拍摄</figcaption></figure><p>在国际类别中，<em>奥本海默</em>再次获得最佳影片奖，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-giamatti">保罗·吉亚玛提</a>则凭借在亚历山大·佩恩的<em>《The Holdovers》</em>中的表演获得最佳国际男演员奖。</p><p>格莱斯顿错过了最佳国际女演员奖，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emma-stone">艾玛·斯通</a>因在欧格斯·兰斯莫斯的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/poor-things-review-emma-stone-yorgos-lanthimos-sex-comedy-3569226"><em>可怜的事情》</em></a>中的表演而再次获得认可，她已经在本颁奖季获得了奥斯卡奖、英国电影学院奖和金球奖的最佳女主角奖。</p><p>自从<em>《奥本海默》</em>上映以来，墨菲的成功最近已经超出了表演范围，本月早些时候，墨菲被透露为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-new-face-versace-anne-hathaway-3612926#:~:text=Cillian%20Murphy%20has%20been%20announced,new%20collection%20campaign%2C%20Versace%20Icons.">范思哲新广告活动的代言人</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-irish-acting-prize-oppenheimer-oscars-3749256">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 为奥斯卡颁奖典礼增添了爱尔兰最高表演奖的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
